    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场穿越诡异、不断变化空间的动作冒险恐怖体验。解开谜题，发现线索，依靠一部神秘手机突破禁锢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你醒来时被困、迷失方向、孤身一人。附近躺着一部手机——你唯一的光源、方向指引和前进手段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333410/extras/55832210fbf2fcef9dbc594d4d337f50.poster.avif?t=1770678472\" width=1170 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333410/extras/55832210fbf2fcef9dbc594d4d337f50.webm?t=1770678472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333410/extras/55832210fbf2fcef9dbc594d4d337f50.mp4?t=1770678472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的逃脱之路穿过一系列令人不安的地点，每一处都比前一处更加压抑。废弃的建筑、广阔华丽的空间、密集的工业走廊，以及在规模和寂静上都显得超现实的区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333410/extras/a8acdfbb7de8f4b7ff3cd7f7e1b17c5d.poster.avif?t=1770678472\" width=1170 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333410/extras/a8acdfbb7de8f4b7ff3cd7f7e1b17c5d.webm?t=1770678472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333410/extras/a8acdfbb7de8f4b7ff3cd7f7e1b17c5d.mp4?t=1770678472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手机是生存的关键。管理它的电量至关重要。恢复电力会开启新的道路。充电标志着你的进展，让你能够深入未知领域。一路上，环境谜题挑战你的洞察力，而突如其来的高压场景则考验你的反应速度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333410/extras/9681ee121bd52e31e4dd73aa0815a196.poster.avif?t=1770678472\" width=1170 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333410/extras/9681ee121bd52e31e4dd73aa0815a196.webm?t=1770678472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333410/extras/9681ee121bd52e31e4dd73aa0815a196.mp4?t=1770678472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>等待你的内容:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特、精心打造的环境，紧张感不断升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于手机的游戏系统，用于照明、供电和检查点</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境和时间谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突发的追逐场景，犹豫将受到惩罚</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;时间正在流逝。&quot;</i></p>",
